            <p>SURVEY CONTEST - RULES AND REGULATIONS<br/>
Winner(s) will be contacted via e-mail or by telephone. Must be 18 years or older to WIN. Only one survey entry per person. Contest is not open to Merivale Mall Employees, Bentall Kennedy (Canada) Limited Partnership Employees, Family Members & Affiliated Agencies. No purchase is necessary. Winner(s) will be selected in a random drawing from among all survey entries received. Chances of winning depends on total number of survey entries received. Winner(s) will be required to present proof of age (Must be 18 years or older to WIN) and will be required to sign an affidavit of eligibility and release of liability. A correctly answered skill testing question may be required. All entrants must abide by these contest rules. Decision of Merivale Mall Management is final.</p>
    
